Package org.gbif.api.model.metrics.cube

Class Dimension<T>

java.lang.Object
org.gbif.api.model.metrics.cube.Dimension<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The value type supported for the dimension
public class Dimension<T> extends Object
A typed dimension to a cube, which is constructed with a unique key. This key defines the HTTP parameter name during serialization, and the type is respected by the ReadBuilder during lookups.
